segments.text: Hello everybody, this is Takanashi Kiara from Hololive English and I'm here to announce
that I have been chosen as an ambassador for Vice Schwartz! Yay! I'm very honored to be
in such a position and I hope that with me and the other ambassadors power together we
can share Vice Schwartz all over the world and we can spread the love and interest for
it to get more and more people to play it, yeah, with us!
i heard that a whole life cards are pretty powerful and my cards especially
so yeah we guys are gonna use them to play with them and i also want to practice a lot to get
really good if possible yeah so i'm gonna do my best let's celebrate the 15 year anniversary of
vice strats together and let's vice strats yay
